############## Deployment_service.yaml file.
We have configured the below requests and limits in the Deployment file.
spec:
      containers:
      - name: my-app
        image: nginx
        resources:
          requests:
            cpu: "100m"
            memory: "128Mi"
          limits:
            cpu: "500m"
            memory: "512Mi"
